text: ao mi td ruom montir khoumkheang teangpir robsakhnhom. rie mneak nei anak teangpir ku nung chak sra aoy chawhvay brosa robsa ke rie mneaktiet trauv kech ng chhkang haey mean satv mk choeksai kbal robsa ke . ruengreav del trauv ban ke vinichchhy nih vea teaktng tow nung avei del anak teangpir suor
